    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single-condition testing; this shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given the direct correspondence between the validation condition and the COU condition. All three QoIs satisfy acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96, relative error < 10%). The credibility assessment supports use of the FEA framework for the regulatory submission. Note: validation results were generated under model configuration ansys-mechanical-2024q3-noncannulated (modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2); the current model version of record is 2026-q1-build-7.",
